'''費伊薩·利勒沙'''（'''Feyisa Lilesa'''，{{bd|1990年|2月1日||}}）是一名[[衣索比亞|衣索比亞]][[田徑|田徑]]運動員，專攻長跑項目<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.iaaf.org/athletes/ethiopia/feyisa-lilesa-240626 |title=Feyisa Lilesa |publisher=IAAF |date=2016-05-23 |accessdate=2016-05-23 |archive-date=2019-04-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190405230935/https://www.iaaf.org/athletes/ethiopia/feyisa-lilesa-240626 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他是[[2011年世界田徑錦標賽|2011年世界田徑錦標賽]]男子馬拉松季軍，也是2016年[[東京馬拉松|東京馬拉松]]男子冠軍。以2小时9分54秒的成绩获得2016年[[里约奥运会|里约奥运会]]男子马拉松[[银牌|银牌]]<ref name="Oromo">{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-37154374 |title=Ethiopia 'hero' runner gets asylum donations after Oromo protest sign |accessdate=22 August 2016 |work=BBC News |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108182853/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-37154374 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.siitube.com/articles/us-state-us-state-department-speaks-about-feyisa-speaks_3010.html|title=U.S. STATE DEPARTMENT SPEAKS ABOUT FEYISA - SiiTube.com - BREAKING #Oromo and #Ethiopia News and Music Video|access-date=2016-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160828220542/https://www.siitube.com/articles/us-state-us-state-department-speaks-about-feyisa-speaks_3010.html|archive-date=2016-08-28|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

2021年11月，面對[[提格雷人民解放阵线|提格雷叛軍]]逐漸逼近首都亞的斯亞貝巴，利勒沙表示願意走上前線拯救自己的國家<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-59393463 |title=Ethiopia's Haile Gebrselassie and Feyisa Lilesa ready to join Tigray war |publisher=BBC |date=2021-11-24}}</ref>。

